ract<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n777由細到大都係考第一既品學兼優乖毒學生，佢做平條狗真係啱曬，由細到大都唔洗同人鬥，鬥都係鬥讀書鬥做好自己果part，邊會理對家係點先出招<br />\n<br />\n689真係另一回事，你睇下佔中3子 G phone，全部都無好下場。用d咩周庸李思嫣，對面黃，自己就整個藍，大量維穩費叫人撐自己，撐下撐下對面散鳩埋就逐一擊破。<br />\n今日照版煮碗，何君 白衫 警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢班condom真係死有餘辜，但背後大撚樣真係689<br />\n第一二個比佢用陰招整死既係香港賢士曾蔭權 同豬西唐英年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc5f395a3323b11a1932a307c5dfe7902d2bccc","tid":1470073,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"869658e3524b8da97e28a57ab36645b6cd22e070","tid":1470073,"uid":208946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"點解佢做國家領導人做到咁得閒。日日數蘋果又懸紅又向企業施壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"政治閒人，比個位有名無實，冇野係佢實則管理只係個名好似好高級咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59748d2d00d62110413846241eb17bcc949f130","tid":1470073,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚得閒 貪咗咁多錢真係唔洗做"},{"pid":"249b1e1e2866c2981c542185380351c328466b97","tid":1470073,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CU68y76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCU68y76.jpg&h=16d0829e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果首席fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}